00:41:23.393 --> 00:41:28.393
And I'm actually curious to kind of hear people's feedback on what they like or don't like about LMSs.

00:41:28.393 --> 00:41:30.393
Learning management system, by the way.

00:41:30.393 --> 00:41:32.393
Learning management system.

00:41:32.393 --> 00:41:38.393
So probably about two years ago, I went to leadership and I was like, hey, I am very interested.

00:41:38.393 --> 00:41:40.393
