00:41:53.393 --> 00:42:01.393
And at the time, we were looking to purchase a service called SkillJar, which is probably one of the more popular learning management systems out there.

00:42:01.393 --> 00:42:05.393
SkillJar is kind of underneath the suite of GainSite tools.

00:42:05.393 --> 00:42:11.393
