00:42:17.393 --> 00:42:20.393
And I wasn't able to answer all those questions on like the business case there.

00:42:20.393 --> 00:42:22.393
And so eventually it kind of fell flat.

00:42:22.393 --> 00:42:28.393
And that was a good learning experience for me, like how to go through that process of developing a business case.

00:42:28.393 --> 00:42:31.393
