00:42:36.393 --> 00:42:45.393
And part of the reason why we created that customer and partner education team was to develop a learning management system where we can deliver on-demand content.

00:42:45.393 --> 00:42:51.393
So at that point, it was much more less on my shoulders to create a business case because now it was like top down.

00:42:51.393 --> 00:42:55.393
Like our leadership's like, hey, Ryan and team, we want you to do this.

00:42:55.393 --> 00:42:59.393
And I was like, great, I wanted to do it a year ago, but let's do it now.

00:42:59.393 --> 00:43:02.393
So I'm very happy like we got there.

00:43:02.393 --> 00:43:04.393
